        "name": "Earth and Sky",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "You erupt into the air with the force of a dragon taking flight, launching nearby creatures into the sky with you. This spell has no effect unless you\u2019re on solid ground when you cast it. You fly directly upward, up to 100 feet into the air. When the spell ends, you safely float to the ground, as *gentle landing*. Every other creature in the area when you Cast this Spell must attempt a Fortitude saving throw.",
